item.title: ZIWE - RERUN
item.description: This week, Kevin is joined by Comedian, Writer and Model, Ziwe! She shares her unique path to creating her own seat at the table. A truly fun conversation that touches on everything from Ziwe's inspirations to Nigerian slang. Feed: https://feeds.simplecast.com/ijknOKeU

item.title: Ep. 266: Is Biden Getting Tough On Bibi? ft. Assal Rad
item.description:
Assal Rad, a Middle East scholar and analyst, joins us to talk about Joe Biden’s conversation with Benjamin Netanyahu, the pressure and leverage Biden can use over Israel, the fallout from the WCK strike and much more.
